Class Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.pareto_enum.maxima_compute.Vector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Vector>

    public class Vector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Vector>
    This class defines the Vector object. It stores the vector as an array and it also provides a set features including rank, DOMINATED and etc that will be explained in their corresponding methods.
